				<outline text="How to tune into BloggerCon" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 12:08:08 GMT">
					<outline text="Whether you're remote or local, you can participate in BloggerCon in many ways." created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 12:08:14 GMT"/>
					<outline text="1. Tune into the IRC at irc.freenode.net/bloggercon." created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 12:08:37 GMT"/>
					<outline text="2. Or the &lt;a href=&quot;http://smartstr.wm.llnwd.net/smartstr_liveces&quot;&gt;webcast&lt;/a&gt;. (Murphy-willing.)" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 12:14:01 GMT"/>
					<outline text="3. Doc Searls is the technographer. If you're in the conference room, you'll see his outline projected on either side of the room. If you're coming in over IRC and/or the webcast, you can view the outlines in a web browser through the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scripting.com/docNography/&quot;&gt;table of contents&lt;/a&gt;. They are also &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scripting.com/docNography/index.opml&quot;&gt;available in OPML&lt;/a&gt;, so they are &lt;a href=&quot;http://api.activerenderer.com/activeRenderer/render/?src=http%3A//www.scripting.com/docNography/index.opml&amp;template=http%3A//www.questiontheanswer.com/ar/activerendererwithchat.htm&amp;flOutliner=yes&amp;flDisplayHTMLWedge=yes&amp;flTitleLink=true&quot;&gt;viewable&lt;/a&gt; in any environment that works with OPML. One interesting idea to try out is to follow a discussion using the &lt;a href=&quot;http://support.opml.org/stories/storyReader$27&quot;&gt;Instant Outliner&lt;/a&gt; in the OPML Editor. " created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 12:14:24 GMT"/>
					<outline text="4. Listen to some &lt;a href=&quot;http://pod-serve.com/podcasts/show/carnvial-cast&quot;&gt;funky music&lt;/a&gt; and get yo rear end in motion!" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 13:30:11 GMT"/>
					<outline text="5. Listen to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bloggercon.org/2006/06/23#a12084&quot;&gt;MP3s&lt;/a&gt; as they become available." created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 16:15:35 GMT"/>
					<outline text="6. Kevin Marks's &lt;a href=&quot;http://media.ito.com/kevinmarks/bloggercon.mov&quot;&gt;video webcast feed&lt;/a&gt;." created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 20:34:23 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="Jake Ludington" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 18:08:44 GMT">
					<outline text="&lt;img src=&quot;http://images.scripting.com/archiveScriptingCom/2006/06/23/jakeWebcastProducer.jpg&quot; width=&quot;207&quot; height=&quot;224&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;A picture named jakeWebcastProducer.jpg&quot;&gt;" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 18:08:48 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Jake is producing the BloggerCon webcast." created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 18:08:51 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="Rex Hammock, Terry Heaton, Paolo Valdemarin" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 18:14:51 GMT">
					<outline text="&lt;img src=&quot;http://images.scripting.com/archiveScriptingCom/2006/06/23/rexTerryPaolo.jpg&quot; width=&quot;271&quot; height=&quot;301&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;A picture named rexTerryPaolo.jpg&quot;&gt;" created="Fri, 23 Jun 2006 18:15:03 GMT"/>
