				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/06/18/AR2006061800618.html&quot;&gt;Jay Rosen&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;All sites become equidistant from the reader.&quot;" created="Tue, 20 Jun 2006 00:03:08 GMT"/>
